* Alphabetical Participant List for Bib Assignment
* Purpose:          Master lookup for assigning bibs and verifying race categories.
* Multi-Client:     Ideal for running on multiple RSClients to speed up check-in.
* Why Birthdate:    Essential for distinguishing between runners with identical names
*                    (e.g., Sr. vs Jr.) to ensure the right person gets the right bib.
*
* Note: use an empty comparand after <> - a literal "" matches two quote
*       characters, not an empty string, and would exclude nothing.
Select              Last Name
<>
Field               BIB
Field               FIRST NAME
Field               LAST NAME
Field               RACE
Field               BIRTHDATE
Sort                LAST NAME
Sort                FIRST NAME
Destination         Browse